name: Lena and Duckie Prototype
description:
A prototype for a game called Lena and Duckie. Player's play as Lena, a yellow Dino, who is a wannabe adventurer trying to find their way to become a popular hero with their companion, Duckie!

For the exe file, please download it and run it. If windows blocks it, click "Run anyway". It will launch the game.
